init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I've been waiting for this day for a long time, Barack.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: They said we'd be notified of a special "perk"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I've been waiting for you to be ready."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look to your wife, who is still smiling and nods.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look back at the house, you've been in it for 8 years, and it's been your home for the last 20.
